    "asOf": "2020-04-03",
    "date": "2020-07-29T17:49:06Z",
    "text": "Police and Fire Health Care Protection Act of 2020\n\nThis bill revises provisions relating to distributions from the accident or health plans or qualified long-term care insurance contracts of retired public safety officers. Specifically, it eliminates the requirement that in order for plan distributions to be excludible from employee gross income, payment of plan premiums must be made directly to the plan providers."
